&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Architect clean, layered data models (staging intermediate mart) that serve as the single source of truth for league analytics, applying dbt best practices for materialization, testing, and documentation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
